data.thought: S2|H|S1|Behavior niche grid hypothesis. X-axis (execution modality): (1) Static=notebook runs once, produces output (2) Reactive=notebook responds to events/triggers (3) Agentic=notebook has goals, makes decisions, loops (4) Swarm=multiple notebook instances coordinate. Y-axis (integration): (1) Isolated=pure compute, no external deps (2) Observatory=streams state via WS to visualization (3) Container=spawns sandboxed processes (4) Multi-system=orchestrates external services. This gives 16 primary niches. Each can have sub-niches by domain. Starting w/ high-value unexplored regions.
